    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted because ASTM F1717 prescribes a single compression-bending configuration as the regulatory standard, and additional loading configurations are not required for the intended 510(k) submission. Overall credibility is sufficient for Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; hash integrity verified.",
